## Slide 05: Bestiary Entry

```html
<h1>Bestiary: Scaffolding Fallacy</h1>
<p><em>noun</em></p>
<p>The tendency to build elaborate infrastructure before confirming the core use case works.</p>
<table style="margin-top: 1em;">
  <tr><td style="width: 20%;"><strong>Signal</strong></td><td>weeks of setup, zero output</td></tr>
  <tr><td><strong>Antidote</strong></td><td>Ship ugly first. Iterate to pretty.</td></tr>
</table>
```

